snippet.title: Just Dance 4: GamesCom 2012 Trailer [UK]
snippet.description:
More Information on: http://www.justdancegame.com/

With over 40 all-new tracks ranging from Top-charted hits to dance party classics and exciting new game features including a brand new Battle Mode, the party is bigger than ever before! Anyone can Just Dance! Available on WiiU™,Wii™, Kinect and PS Move. Lights Off, Party On !

Out on October 2nd, 2012
